{"tid":2515744,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"菲國外長就發表帶粗口帖文道歉　總統稱中國是恩人","createTime":"2021-05-04T07:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-04T09:23:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"3691dce91871ed2a53d4a8415a5a90ffe568fdee","tid":2515744,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:47:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589150-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589150-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=4vQCcaBbFH%2F4J6PBkjxGnjBOARg6NHmmMIcc3tsY8ek%3D&h=3bb66444\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1589150-20210504.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=261bb5ef\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1589150-20210504.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓外長洛欽就他在社交網站發表帶有粗口的帖文，要求中國船隻離開兩國有主權爭議水域，向中方道歉。<br />\n<br />\n總統府發言人說，洛欽已經向中國大使致歉，又引述洛欽表示，發表有關言論是因為有些事惹怒了他。<br />\n<br />\n總統杜特爾特強調，中國仍然是菲律賓的恩人，雖然菲律賓與中國之間發生衝突，但並不意味菲方要變得無禮，不尊重別人，菲律賓事實上亦有太多事要感謝中國，無論是過去的幫助，或者是現在的協助。<br />\n<br />\n杜特爾特昨日接種中國國藥集團的新冠疫苗，他在接種後表示感覺不錯。"},{"pid":"909a2723c5dce9c33a52506a9bfcc626a1a80200","tid":2515744,"uid":80724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:52:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f911b1c1d581993a1aa1a4493fe5389343b3aa6","tid":2515744,"uid":321977,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:53:35.000Z","msg":"勁共勁共勁共<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/hair.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a3bbfe28bfd7dc56bcda36c5211702cc60f17d1","tid":2515744,"uid":3801,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-04T07:54:25.000Z","msg":"屌完你再講句sor 咁就過到骨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4afe2d4dc563706dd1ff1d2b3ac211d929f6531e","tid":2515744,"uid":7903,"lik